org.jactr.io.compiler

Class AbstractReportableUnitCompiler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jactr.io.compiler.AbstractReportableUnitCompiler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IReportableUnitCompiler, IUnitCompiler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    StrictHarvestingUnitCompiler

    public abstract class AbstractReportableUnitCompiler
extends java.lang.Object
implements IReportableUnitCompiler
    basic abstract IReportableUnitCompiler. Clients should extend and implement compile(CommonTree) from which you will call report(String, CommonTree) with any messages. The actual message and its reporting back to the DefaultCompiler will be handled based on IReportableUnitCompiler.Level.

    This class is not thread safe.
    Author:
    harrison
